<plot>Today is Friday. Juan is desperate. It's his girlfriend's birthday and Juan is busy. He's helping Esteban, a friend, with a chore that's taken too many days. Esteban asks for patience but Juan's anguish grows as his girlfriend keeps calling on the phone. Told through an impressive sequence-shot, POR UNA PERRA is a story about anguish and desperation... in real time.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?439296</url></doc>
